text: This is a list of every officeholders of the Republic of Yucatán ==Officeholders== Francisco Antonio Tarrazo April 23, 1824-1825 (interim) Santiago Méndez August 22, 1840-June 2, 1844 José Tiburcio López Constante June 2, 1844 – January 1, 1846 Domingo Barret January 21, 1847 – October 3, 1847 Miguel Barbachano y Tarrazo October 3, 1847-July 14, 1848
title: List of Presidents of the Republic of Yucatán
